
Documentation is being worked on, but for the time being look in the docs/
directory.  Start with the README to find out about all the commands.

To see the differences from mcl-0.52.99, look at the ChangeLog.

To see what we're working on, look at Notes.

To get started, copy the contents of the samples/ directory to a directory
~/.dirt/.  Configuration variables are stored in ~/.dirt/dirtrc and
~/.dirt/Saved.pl (from perl).
